      <guid>https://playbook.digitalmaneuver.com/introduction/what-is-software-development.html</guid>
      <description>Topics Most software projects are things being built for the first time. There is a high level of uniqueness in each project. Even if the tools and process is the same, the logic and business process to be mapped and solved is not.
Small iterations, incremental value, low risk.
Forecasting, planning, and budgeting software projects. Note, you can only do this if you&amp;rsquo;ve done the same project before. If it&amp;rsquo;s a new domain, estimates and budgets will be incorrect.</description>
